query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(mi_idx it2) NoHashJoin(it2 mi_idx mk t k) NoMergeJoin(it2 k kt mi_idx mk t mi) NoMergeJoin(it2 k kt mi mi_idx mk t it1) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS western_dark_production
from movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND mi_idx.info > '11' AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ( t.title like '%murder%' OR t.title like '%Murder%' OR t.title like '%Mord%') AND t.production_year > 2009
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('character-name-in-title',
'shot-multiple-times')
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'episode'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Norwegian',
'English',
'American',
'Swedish',
'Bulgaria',
'USA',
'Danish',
'Denmark',
'German',
'USA')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries';
